# Butler Theme Specifications

## Color Palette

TheButler maintains a sophisticated butler aesthetic with these exact colors:

### Primary Colors
- **Charcoal**: #1a1a2e (Primary dark color)
- **Charcoal Light**: #2c2c44 (Hover states)
- **Gold**: #d4af37 (Accent color)
- **Gold Light**: #dfc159 (Hover states)
- **Cream**: #f5f5f0 (Light backgrounds)
- **White**: #ffffff (Surface)

### Color Admin Integration
- **Sidebar BG**: #2d353c (Color Admin gray-800)
- **Sidebar Dark**: #242a30 (Color Admin darker)
- **Content BG**: #f2f3f4 (Color Admin light)
- **Text Dark**: #242a30 (Color Admin text)

### Status Colors
- **Success**: #2d7a4f (Green) or #32a932 (Color Admin green)
- **Warning**: #f4a261 (Orange) or #f59c1a (Color Admin orange)
- **Error**: #e63946 (Red)
- **Info**: #457b9d (Blue) or #348fe2 (Color Admin blue)

## Where to Use Each Color

### Gold (#d4af37)
- Active menu items (sidebar)
- Accent buttons
- Primary action buttons
- Badge backgrounds
- Links and hover states
- Input focus borders
- Chart primary series

### Charcoal (#1a1a2e, #2d353c)
- Sidebar background
- Top brand section
- Dark card variants
- Primary buttons (alternative)
- Text on gold backgrounds

### Gray Scales
- **#242a30**: Main text, headers
- **#666**: Secondary text, icons
- **#f2f3f4**: Content background
- **rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)**: Subtle borders

## Typography

### Font Families
```scss
--font-family-primary: 'Crimson Text', 'Georgia', serif;  // Headers, brand
--font-family-secondary: 'Inter', sans-serif;              // Body, UI
```

### Font Weights
- **Light (300)**: Page headers
- **Normal (400)**: Body text
- **Medium (500)**: Links, buttons
- **Semi-bold (600)**: Card headers, menu items
- **Bold (700)**: Important numbers, badges

### Font Sizes (Color Admin Standard)
- **Page Headers**: 28px
- **Card Headers**: 16px
- **Body Text**: 13-14px
- **Menu Items**: 13.5px
- **Breadcrumbs**: 12px
- **Small Text**: 11px
- **Badges**: 10px

## Spacing (Color Admin Standard)

- **Grid gaps**: 15px
- **Card padding**: 20px
- **Card margins**: 15px bottom
- **Section spacing**: 20-25px
- **Form field gaps**: 20px vertical
- **Button gaps**: 10px

## Shadows

Match Color Admin's subtle approach:
- **Cards**: `0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)`
- **Card Hover**: `0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)`
- **Topbar**: `0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)`
- **Dialogs**: `0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)`
- **Dropdowns**: `0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)`

## Border Radius

- **Cards**: 6px
- **Buttons**: 6px
- **Inputs**: 6px
- **Dialogs**: 6px
- **Badges**: 12px (pill shape)
- **Avatars**: 50% (circles)

## Button Styles

### Primary (Accent - Gold)
```scss
.btn--accent {
  background: #d4af37;
  color: #1a1a2e;
  
  &:hover {
    background: #dfc159;
  }
}
```

### Secondary (Charcoal)
```scss
.btn--primary {
  background: #1a1a2e;
  color: #f5f5f0;
  
  &:hover {
    background: #2c2c44;
  }
}
```

### Outline
```scss
.btn--outline {
  background: transparent;
  border: 2px solid #1a1a2e;
  color: #1a1a2e;
  
  &:hover {
    background: #1a1a2e;
    color: #f5f5f0;
  }
}
```

## Badge Styles

```scss
.badge {
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  
  &--success { background: rgba(45, 122, 79, 0.1); color: #2d7a4f; }
  &--warning { background: rgba(244, 162, 97, 0.1); color: #f4a261; }
  &--error { background: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.1); color: #e63946; }
  &--info { background: rgba(69, 123, 157, 0.1); color: #457b9d; }
}
```

## Active States

### Menu Items (Sidebar)
```scss
.menu-item--active {
  .menu-link {
    background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
    color: #d4af37;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-left: 3px solid #d4af37;
  }
}
```

### Links
```scss
a:hover {
  color: #d4af37; // Gold hover
}
```

## Transitions

Standard transition timings:
- **Fast**: 150ms (hover effects)
- **Base**: 250ms (state changes)
- **Slow**: 350ms (complex animations)
- **Easing**: ease-in-out

## CSS Custom Properties

Reference: [styles.scss](mdc:src/styles.scss)

All butler colors are available as CSS variables:
- `var(--color-primary)`: #1a1a2e
- `var(--color-accent)`: #d4af37
- `var(--color-background)`: #f5f5f0
- `var(--color-surface)`: #ffffff

Use these for consistency across components.

